At 5th level, when attempting to damage objects and structures, he ignores the first 5 points of hardness.
At 8th level, the demolitionist gains a +2 insight bonus on attack rolls when attempting to sunder an item.
At 11th level, he can attempt a sunder combat maneuver check against a wall no more than 5 feet thick. If the damage from the sunder combat maneuver exceeds the wall's hardness, the demolitionist creates a 5-foot opening in the wall, through which a Medium creature can easily pass.ª<
